zcrc is header-only and can be used from CMake via:

  # To consume the library as a header (#include <zcrc/zcrc.hpp>):
  find_package(zcrc CONFIG REQUIRED)
  target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE zcrc::zcrc)

  # To consume the library as a module (import zcrc;):
  find_package(zcrc CONFIG REQUIRED COMPONENTS module)
  target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE zcrc::zcrc-module)

zcrc provides pkg-config modules:

  zcrc
